issue that caused a deep rift in the western alliance that was 
patched over last month 
if it became clear that nato countries are ready to join us in 
negotiations on tactical nuclear weapons we could naturally after 
consulting our allies carry out without delay further unilateral 
reductions in our tactical nuclear missiles in europe gorbachev 
