with the hanoisponsored hun sen regime are crucial to the 
achievement of a viable political accord and we urge our asean 
friends to use their unity to strengthen the princes position as he 
seeks to advance the process of national reconciliation 
the main barrier is refusal of the provietnam government to let 
the khmer rouge join in a provisional fourparty government the 
khmer rouge reportedly is storing arms for a major push once the 
vietnamese soldiers leave 
baker said washington will stay engaged in the region as it 
faces these and other challenges east asia is integral to 
americas future he said 
mitsuzuka also opposed what asean officials now commonly refer to 
as an afghanistantype solution 
