degrees the final step is to bore through molten and partially 
molten rock with a bit that sprays some sort of liquid to clean the 
bit and cool the rock to drillable consistancy 
fluid would continue to be flushed through the well and through 
fractures in the solidified magma possibly generating highpressure 
steam that would be used to drive turbine generators at ground level 
