and its major bankruptcy creditors it was opposed by pension 
benefit guaranty corp 
at issue were monthly payments for 965 retirees and beneficiaries 
that have been paid for about 2 years under an agreement between 
the company and the pbgc the federally established insurer of 
private pension plans 
