percent of the outstanding shares 
the government began its sale of air canada last october when it 
sold 308 million shares or about 43 percent of the company for 8 
a share 
the sale will raise about 490 million which is expected to go 
to the government rather than the airline the 240 million in 
proceeds from the october sale went to paying air canadas debt 
there was a sixmonth period in which no sales were allowed of 
the government shares mcdermid said weve passed that now and 
the market conditions and the circumstances of air canada now permit 
the balance of shares to be sold 
the lead underwriter in the share issue rbc dominion securities 
recommended to the government wednesday what the share price should 
be and how many shares should be sold 
mcdermid said in an interview the 12ashare offering price 
represents a good return to the government although he had hinted 
in may that the price could be as high as 16 
air canada stock had been trading on the montreal and toronto 
exchanges at around 13 a share but closed wednesday before 
mcdermids announcement at 1225 
the price began to rise shortly after the stock was issued in 
october but it soared in january after pwa corp announced it was 
buying wardair that meant the number of canadian airline companies 
dropped from three to two and the reduced competition made air 
canada a darling of the financial community 
the carrier can operate in the private sector much better than 
in the public sector mcdermid said it will be allowed to 
compete on an open and free basis rather than having government 
dictate to it 
mcdermid said all shares have been committed to be purchased from 
the government by underwriters who in turn sell them to investors 
he said 33 million shares will be issued in canada and 8 million to 
foreigners 
octobers sale was restricted to canadians but foreign investors 
soon began to buy them from canadians willing to sell foreign 
investors are now edging toward the 25 percent ceiling on foreign 
ownership of a canadian airline 
mcdermid did not say when the sale will take place octobers 
sale occurred 2 weeks after the prospectus was issued 
